{"tid":2440972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國指中國種族滅絕新疆維族人　中方批評美方撒謊","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T00:20:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9b6c0b272bdd562fe7d0ee21dab62ebdb5ff92","tid":2440972,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"美國指中國種族滅絕新疆維族人　中方批評美方撒謊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579805-20210310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579805-20210310.htm&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=b6472995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579805-20210310.htm&h=1770df3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579805-20210310.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人普萊斯早前表示，中國對新疆維吾爾族人犯下種族滅絕與反人類罪行。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅批評說法荒謬絕倫，與事實完全相反，是別有用心的造謠和徹頭徹尾的謊言，要求美方拿出證據。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅重申，新疆維吾爾族人口從555萬增長到1200多萬，質疑種族滅絕的說法。他又諷刺美國殺害印第安人的歷史，暗示「有人更適合戴上種族滅絕的帽子」，認為美方應該首先關注和改善自身存在的人權問題，中方堅決反對在人權問題上撒謊、造謠，打著人權旗號干涉別國內政。"},{"pid":"74702ec0560521c34d970fba2d9b1b7faa4c898f","tid":2440972,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"趙立堅呢個撚樣個樣真係好撚嬲打<br />\n<br />\n賊眉賊眼"},{"pid":"888e128bb2c2166e89daebc88a89c1d1a21f76a4","tid":2440972,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"種族滅絕又點<br />\n有本事咪去斬首囖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDwvjhr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDwvjhr.gif&h=dc44ca25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3fe94683741289a48343b0ea6750d117818ca6c","tid":2440972,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}